General.Name: aovo Touristik AG
General.Description: aovo Touristik AG engages in the provision of tour and travel services primarily in Germany and internationally. The company provides tailor-made and target group-oriented packages, and modular solutions in musicals and shows, concerts and festivals, and cultural events, as well as city, gourmet, and wellness trips. It offers its services under aovo.de, eventreise.de, and musical-mit-hotel.de brand names. The company also provides tour operation and technology services; and markets its services through direct sales and online. aovo Touristik AG was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Hanover, Germany.
